<STYLE>

}

}
label,datalist {

}

label {

}

<body>
    <h1>HTML WEB PAGES</h1>
  <h1 id="table-heading"><bold>TABLLES AND LISTS</bold></h1>
  <Table id="courseTable" style="background-color:#f19bed"class="center">
      <tr>
          <td>ROLLNO</td>
          <Td> NAME</Td>

  </Table>
  <H2 ID="COURSEheading"><bold>NO OF COURSES available</bold></H2>
     <ul ID="courseList"style="list-style-type:circle">
         <li >information technology</li>
         <li>electronics</li>
         <li>computer science</li>
         <li>mechanical</li>
         </ul >
         <h1 id="image heading" ><STRONG>IMAGE MAP</STRONG></h1>
         <img src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/photo/2017/05/11/11/15/workplace-2303851_960_720.jpg" alt="Desk" usemap="#deskmap" width="500" height="380">
         <map name="deskmap">
           <area shape="rect" coords="175,242,420,358" alt="Keyboard" target="_blank"
           href="data:image/jpeg;base64,">
           
           <area shape="rect" coords="444,251,481,357" alt="Mouse" target="_blank" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_mouse">
           
           <area shape="rect" coords="375,14,481,357" alt="Diary" target="_blank" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Book">
         </map>
         <form id="login-form"style="border:BLACK; border-width:1px; border-style:solid;" >
          <H1 style="background-color:#33475b" ><b>form and form elements</b></H1>

          <label >NAME:</label>
           
          <INPUT ID="fNAME">
          
            <LABEL>PASSWORD:</LABEL>
          
            <INPUT ID="PASSWORD:">
          
                <LABEL >EMAIL:</LABEL>
          
                <input id="EMAIL:"> </input>
          
                    <LABEL>COURSES</LABEL>
                    <SELECT NAME="COURSE">
  <OPTION>INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY</OPTION>
  <OPTION>COMPUTER</OPTION>
  <OPTION>MECHANICAL</OPTION>
  <OPTION>ELECTRONICS</OPTION>
</SELECT>
  <LABEL>ADDRESS:</LABEL>
           <textarea id=address></textarea>
           <LABEL>COUNTRY:</LABEL>
           <INPUT ID="COUNTRY">
           <datalist id="countries">
             <OPTION>INDIA</OPTION>
          <OPTION>FRANCE</OPTION>
      <OPTION>CANADA</OPTION>
  <OPTION >UK</OPTION>
  <OPTION>GERMAN</OPTION></datalist>
                   <button id="submit_btn">submit</button>
      </form>
